<li class="comment byuser comment-author-mcrustawildernesscat-com bypostauthor odd alt depth-2" id="li-comment-52066">
<article id="comment-52066" class="comment">
<header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard">
<img alt='small mallory photo' src='https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cropped-Small-pfp-44x44.jpg' srcset='https://allaboutcats.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cropped-Small-pfp-88x88.jpg 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' loading='lazy' decoding='async' /><cite><b class="fn"><a href='https://www.wildernesscat.com/' rel='external nofollow ugc' class='url'>Mallory Crusta</a></b> <span>Post author</span></cite><a href="https://allaboutcats.com/best-cat-brush#comment-52066"><time datetime="2021-05-28T21:34:32+00:00">May 28, 2021 at 9:34 pm</time></a> </header>
<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>Hi Meg, your kitties may feel comfortable with <a href="http://www.furminator.com/legacy-products/cat-shed-control-cloths.aspx" rel="nofollow ugc">Furminator&#8217;s shedding control cloth</a>s, which allow you to stroke your cat with a soft cloth and remove loose hair.</p>
</section>
